@node gtsetlap "XTRU - Setlap Gadget"
XTRU - Set Laps
===============

Press on this gadget and enter a number between 1 and 127 and press return!

You can now race for 127 laps! Please note don't try an alter this on the XTR
Setup Menu, It will let you decrease the laps but not increase them. Also
while playing you will notice that the lap counter will become corrupt with
laps over nine. This is OK, it just means you will have to keep count.
@endnode

